Date: 1994-06-20

Title: Determinant Representations for Correlation Functions of Spin-1/2 XXX

and XXZ Heisenberg MagnetsAuthors: F.H.L. Essler, H. Frahm, A.G. Izergin, V.E. Korepin

Comments: 23 pages, TeX, BONN-TH-94-14, revised version

Journal-ref: Commun.Math.Phys. 174 (1995) 191-214

We consider correlation functions of the spin-$\half$ XXX and XXZ Heisenbergchains in a magnetic field. Starting from the algebraic Bethe Ansatz we deriverepresentations for various correlation functions in terms of determinants ofFredholm integral operators.